ORDER BY [a].[Priority] DESC, [a].[TryCount], [a].[NextTryTime]

SELECT [b].[Id], [b].[AccountNumber], [b].[AvailableBalance], [b].[ClientId], [t].[Id], [t].[Email], [t].[Name], [t].[Pin], [t].[UserType]
FROM [BankAccounts] AS [b]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Email], [p].[Name], [p].[Pin], [p].[UserType]
    FROM [Persons] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[UserType] = N'Client'
) AS [t] ON [b].[ClientId] = [t].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t2].[AccountNumber], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Amount], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id00]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Name], [p].[Id]
    FROM [Persons] AS [p]
    WHERE ([p].[UserType] = N'Client') AND ([p].[Id] = @__clientId_0)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b].[AccountNumber], [b].[Id], [t1].[Amount], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [b].[ClientId]
    FROM [BankAccounts] AS [b]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [t0].[Amount], [b0].[Id], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0]
        FROM [BankAccount_Transactions] AS [b0]
        LEFT JOIN [Transactions] AS [t0] ON [b0].[TransactionId] = [t0].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [b].[Id] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[ClientId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id00]

SELECT [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t2].[AccountNumber], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Amount], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id00]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Name], [p].[Id]
    FROM [Persons] AS [p]
    WHERE ([p].[UserType] = N'Client') AND ([p].[Id] = @__clientId_0)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b].[AccountNumber], [b].[Id], [t1].[Amount], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [b].[ClientId]
    FROM [BankAccounts] AS [b]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [t0].[Amount], [b0].[Id], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0]
        FROM [BankAccount_Transactions] AS [b0]
        LEFT JOIN [Transactions] AS [t0] ON [b0].[TransactionId] = [t0].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [b].[Id] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[ClientId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id00]

SELECT [p].[Name], [p].[Id], [t1].[AccountNumber], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Amount], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id00]
FROM [Persons] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b].[AccountNumber], [b].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t0].[Id0] AS [Id00], [b].[ClientId]
    FROM [BankAccounts] AS [b]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [t].[Amount], [b0].[Id], [t].[Id] AS [Id0]
        FROM [BankAccount_Transactions] AS [b0]
        LEFT JOIN [Transactions] AS [t] ON [b0].[TransactionId] = [t].[Id]
    ) AS [t0] ON [b].[Id] = [t0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [p].[Id] = [t1].[ClientId]
WHERE ([p].[UserType] = N'Client') AND ([p].[Id] = @__clientId_0)
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id00]

FROM [Persons] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b].[AccountNumber], [b].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t0].[Id0] AS [Id00], [b].[ClientId]
    FROM [BankAccounts] AS [b]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [t].[Amount], [b0].[Id], [t].[Id] AS [Id0]
        FROM [BankAccount_Transactions] AS [b0]
        LEFT JOIN [Transactions] AS [t] ON [b0].[TransactionId] = [t].[Id]
    ) AS [t0] ON [b].[Id] = [t0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [p].[Id] = [t1].[ClientId]
WHERE ([p].[UserType] = N'Client') AND ([p].[Id] = @__clientId_0)
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id00]

SELECT [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t2].[AccountNumber], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Amount], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id00]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Name], [p].[Id]
    FROM [Persons] AS [p]
    WHERE ([p].[UserType] = N'Client') AND ([p].[Id] = @__clientId_0)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b].[AccountNumber], [b].[Id], [t1].[Amount], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [b].[ClientId]
    FROM [BankAccounts] AS [b]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [t0].[Amount], [b0].[Id], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0]
        FROM [BankAccount_Transactions] AS [b0]
        LEFT JOIN [Transactions] AS [t0] ON [b0].[TransactionId] = [t0].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [b].[Id] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[ClientId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id00]

SELECT [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t2].[AccountNumber], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Amount], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id00]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Name], [p].[Id]
    FROM [Persons] AS [p]
    WHERE ([p].[UserType] = N'Client') AND ([p].[Id] = @__clientId_0)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b].[AccountNumber], [b].[Id], [t1].[Amount], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [b].[ClientId]
    FROM [BankAccounts] AS [b]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [t0].[Amount], [b0].[Id], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0]
        FROM [BankAccount_Transactions] AS [b0]
        LEFT JOIN [Transactions] AS [t0] ON [b0].[TransactionId] = [t0].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [b].[Id] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[ClientId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id00]

INFO  2022-04-21 13:33:26,418 [7    ] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (31ms) [Parameters=[@__clientId_0='?' (DbType = Guid)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t2].[AccountNumber], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Amount], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id00]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Name], [p].[Id]
    FROM [Persons] AS [p]
    WHERE ([p].[UserType] = N'Client') AND ([p].[Id] = @__clientId_0)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b].[AccountNumber], [b].[Id], [t1].[Amount], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [b].[ClientId]
    FROM [BankAccounts] AS [b]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [t0].[Amount], [b0].[Id], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0]
        FROM [BankAccount_Transactions] AS [b0]
        LEFT JOIN [Transactions] AS [t0] ON [b0].[TransactionId] = [t0].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [b].[Id] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[ClientId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id00]

INFO  2022-04-21 13:35:28,748 [4    ] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (25ms) [Parameters=[@__clientId_0='?' (DbType = Guid)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t2].[AccountNumber], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Amount], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id00]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Name], [p].[Id]
    FROM [Persons] AS [p]
    WHERE ([p].[UserType] = N'Client') AND ([p].[Id] = @__clientId_0)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b].[AccountNumber], [b].[Id], [t1].[Amount], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [b].[ClientId]
    FROM [BankAccounts] AS [b]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [t0].[Amount], [b0].[Id], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0]
        FROM [BankAccount_Transactions] AS [b0]
        LEFT JOIN [Transactions] AS [t0] ON [b0].[TransactionId] = [t0].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [b].[Id] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[ClientId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id00]

SELECT [t].[Name], [t].[Id], [t2].[AccountNumber], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Amount], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id00]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Name], [p].[Id]
    FROM [Persons] AS [p]
    WHERE ([p].[UserType] = N'Client') AND ([p].[Id] = @__clientId_0)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b].[AccountNumber], [b].[Id], [t1].[Amount], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [b].[ClientId]
    FROM [BankAccounts] AS [b]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [t0].[Amount], [b0].[Id], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0]
        FROM [BankAccount_Transactions] AS [b0]
        LEFT JOIN [Transactions] AS [t0] ON [b0].[TransactionId] = [t0].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [b].[Id] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[ClientId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Id00]

FROM [Persons] AS [p]

INFO  2022-04-21 14:42:47,431 [12   ] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (19ms) [Parameters=[@__clientId_0='?' (DbType = Guid)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [p].[Name], [p].[Id], [t1].[AccountNumber], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Amount], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id00], [t1].[Id1]
FROM [Persons] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b].[AccountNumber], [b].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t0].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t0].[Id1], [b].[ClientId]
    FROM [BankAccounts] AS [b]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [t].[Amount], [b0].[Id], [b1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t].[Id] AS [Id1]
        FROM [BankAccount_Transactions] AS [b0]
        LEFT JOIN [BankAccounts] AS [b1] ON [b0].[BankAccountId] = [b1].[Id]
        LEFT JOIN [Transactions] AS [t] ON [b0].[TransactionId] = [t].[Id]
    ) AS [t0] ON [b].[Id] = [t0].[Id0]
) AS [t1] ON [p].[Id] = [t1].[ClientId]
WHERE ([p].[UserType] = N'Client') AND ([p].[Id] = @__clientId_0)
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id00], [t1].[Id1]

INFO  2022-04-21 14:43:50,697 [12   ] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (15ms) [Parameters=[@__clientId_0='?' (DbType = Guid)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [p].[Name], [p].[Id], [t1].[AccountNumber], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Amount], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id00], [t1].[Id1]
FROM [Persons] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b].[AccountNumber], [b].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t0].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t0].[Id1], [b].[ClientId]
    FROM [BankAccounts] AS [b]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [t].[Amount], [b0].[Id], [b1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t].[Id] AS [Id1]
        FROM [BankAccount_Transactions] AS [b0]
        LEFT JOIN [BankAccounts] AS [b1] ON [b0].[BankAccountId] = [b1].[Id]
        LEFT JOIN [Transactions] AS [t] ON [b0].[TransactionId] = [t].[Id]
    ) AS [t0] ON [b].[Id] = [t0].[Id0]
) AS [t1] ON [p].[Id] = [t1].[ClientId]
WHERE ([p].[UserType] = N'Client') AND ([p].[Id] = @__clientId_0)
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id00], [t1].[Id1]

SELECT [p].[Name], [p].[Id], [t1].[AccountNumber], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Amount], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id00], [t1].[Id1]
FROM [Persons] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b].[AccountNumber], [b].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t0].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t0].[Id1], [b].[ClientId]
    FROM [BankAccounts] AS [b]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [t].[Amount], [b0].[Id], [b1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t].[Id] AS [Id1]
        FROM [BankAccount_Transactions] AS [b0]
        LEFT JOIN [BankAccounts] AS [b1] ON [b0].[BankAccountId] = [b1].[Id]
        LEFT JOIN [Transactions] AS [t] ON [b0].[TransactionId] = [t].[Id]
    ) AS [t0] ON [b].[Id] = [t0].[Id0]
) AS [t1] ON [p].[Id] = [t1].[ClientId]
WHERE ([p].[UserType] = N'Client') AND ([p].[Id] = @__clientId_0)
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id00], [t1].[Id1]

SELECT [p].[Name], [p].[Id], [t1].[AccountNumber], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Amount], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id00], [t1].[Id1]
FROM [Persons] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b].[AccountNumber], [b].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t0].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t0].[Id1], [b].[ClientId]
    FROM [BankAccounts] AS [b]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [t].[Amount], [b0].[Id], [b1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t].[Id] AS [Id1]
        FROM [BankAccount_Transactions] AS [b0]
        LEFT JOIN [BankAccounts] AS [b1] ON [b0].[BankAccountId] = [b1].[Id]
        LEFT JOIN [Transactions] AS [t] ON [b0].[TransactionId] = [t].[Id]
    ) AS [t0] ON [b].[Id] = [t0].[Id0]
) AS [t1] ON [p].[Id] = [t1].[ClientId]
WHERE ([p].[UserType] = N'Client') AND ([p].[Id] = @__clientId_0)
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id00], [t1].[Id1]

SELECT [p].[Name], [p].[Id], [t1].[AccountNumber], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Amount], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id00], [t1].[Id1]
FROM [Persons] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b].[AccountNumber], [b].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t0].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t0].[Id1], [b].[ClientId]
    FROM [BankAccounts] AS [b]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [t].[Amount], [b0].[Id], [b1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t].[Id] AS [Id1]
        FROM [BankAccount_Transactions] AS [b0]
        LEFT JOIN [BankAccounts] AS [b1] ON [b0].[BankAccountId] = [b1].[Id]
        LEFT JOIN [Transactions] AS [t] ON [b0].[TransactionId] = [t].[Id]
    ) AS [t0] ON [b].[Id] = [t0].[Id0]
) AS [t1] ON [p].[Id] = [t1].[ClientId]
WHERE ([p].[UserType] = N'Client') AND ([p].[Id] = @__clientId_0)
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id00], [t1].[Id1]
